				</listitem>
			</varlistentry>
			<varlistentry>
				<term><constant>GL_FUNC_REVERSE_SUBTRACT</constant></term>
				<listitem>
					<simpara>
						Is like <constant>GL_FUNC_ADD</constant> except the product of the source factor and the source color is
						componentwise subtracted from the product of the destination factor and the destination color. The result
						is clamped to the range <inlineequation>
							<mml:math>
								<mml:mfenced open="[" close="]">
									<mml:mn>0</mml:mn>
									<mml:mn>1</mml:mn>
								</mml:mfenced>
							</mml:math>
						</inlineequation>.
					</simpara>
					<informalequation>
						<mml:math>
							<mml:mtable>
								<mml:mtr>
